<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd" identifier="prisma-recto-diagonal-arista-faltante" title="Diagonal de un prisma recto y arista faltante" adaptive="false" time-dependent="false">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>La diagonal de un prisma recto de base rectangular se calcula como <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
        <msqrt>
          <mrow>
            <msup>
              <mi>a</mi>
              <mn>2</mn>
            </msup>
            <mo>+</mo>
            <msup>
              <mi>b</mi>
              <mn>2</mn>
            </msup>
            <mo>+</mo>
            <msup>
              <mi>c</mi>
              <mn>2</mn>
            </msup>
          </mrow>
        </msqrt>
      </math>, con a, b y c las medidas de sus aristas.</p>
    <p>Considera que la diagonal de un prisma recto de base rectangular mide <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
        <msqrt>
          <mn>83</mn>
        </msqrt>
      </math> cm y que dos de sus aristas miden <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
        <mn>3</mn>
      </math> cm y <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
        <mn>5</mn>
      </math> cm.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices="1" response-identifier="RESPONSE">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuánto mide la arista faltante?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
          <mn>4</mn>
        </math> cm
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
          <mn>7</mn>
        </math> cm
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
          <mn>19</mn>
        </math> cm
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
          <mn>49</mn>
        </math> cm
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing template="https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml" />
</qti-assessment-item>